data.title: National Museum of Natural History
data.meta_description: Discover the National Museum of Natural History in Paris and book all your tickets and guided tours to the Galleries of the Jardin des Plantes, Botanical Parks and Zoos, and The Museum of Man.
data.text:
Activities

Paris city tour, Seine cruise and Eiffel Tower skip-the-line tickets

See iconic Paris with Eiffel Tower priority tickets, luxury air-conditioned coach transport, a Seine cruise and a multilingual guide. A perfect introduction!

Activities

Lunch cruise on the River Seine

Board at the foot at the Eiffel Tower for a 2-hour authentic and unforgettable Lunch Cruise along the River Seine in central Paris.

Activities

Dinner cruise on the river Seine

Sail in a glassed-over boat for a 2.5-hours à-la-carte meal dinner cruise and enjoy an unforgettable dinner while discovering the secrets of Paris and its light.

Attractions & guided tours

Impressionist masterpieces at Orsay Museum small group tour

Get your skip-the-line tickets and guided tour of the highlights of the Orsay Museum, and visit the world's largest collection of impressionist art.

Attractions & guided tours

Entrance ticket Grévin Wax Museum Paris

Buy your Grévin Museum Paris - Entrance Ticket with Musement with our price match guarantee and secure booking. Get informed, plan and book your amazing activities in Paris.

Attractions & guided tours

Montparnasse tower 56th floor tickets

Book your ticket for the Tour Montparnasse and go up to the 56th floor of the tower to enjoy the best panoramic view of Paris!

Attractions & guided tours

Visit of the Louvre Museum and cruise ticket

Get your ticket to the Louvre Museum and a 1-hour cruise on the Seine river.

Attractions & guided tours

Moulin Rouge show tickets

Buy your Moulin Rouge Show tickets: Live a dream night in an iconic setting and discover a different side of Paris's famous landmarks by night.

Activities

Paris City tour and Moulin Rouge show

Discover the charm of the French capital with a bus tour and admire the fun and sensual show at the Moulin Rouge.

Activities

Paris: Guided Bike Tour with Food Tasting

Discover the places Parisians are used to go to and taste french food during this bike tour.

Attractions & guided tours

Paris city tour

Book a city tour of Paris in an open-top coach, the ideal activity for first-time visitors in Paris. Several departures a day leave from our agency located near the Louvre.

Activities

Best of Paris guided bike tour

Buy your Best of Paris guided bike tour now with a guide and whiz through the Parisian streets learning about the best monuments.

Attractions & guided tours

Entrance ticket to the Opéra Garnier

Buy your entrance ticket to the Palais Garnier, the famous Opéra de Paris, and visit one of the city's most significant architectural gems.
